&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;Looking at&#160;~/collections/&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;collection-overview&lt;/tt&gt; show the correct state. But many operators are used to looking at graph view for a quick overview to find issues.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
